<F P=100> Mongolia </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Political Consensus' Document Signed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    `Political Consensus' Document Signed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2204093094 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1654 
GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2204093094 </F>
